snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you, Thank you, Thank you Jaffer Zaidi for such an wonderful lyric and all the musicians who played for this masterpiece. Kaavish & Quratulain Balouch's voice shatters my heart and soul into pieces every time, especially from 4:14 when Kaavish sings 'Dharke ye dil tere hi liye' and that music of violin takes me to an emotional roller coaster ride that I have no words for. my heart couldn't take "Ja raha hu main" for a long time, still can't. 

One of the greatest emotional songs ever created <3
